ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
PrecisAppointment of GILLES PATRY, C.M., O.Ont., of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of John K. Bell, whose term has expired.
